This character is being interrogated by a thug of Callik's in the basement of the Seedy Tavern. She has initial selected, seconday, and secondary if threatened.

She gives the player a locket to open the Silver sails. 

She is invulnerable until after the thugs in the room are dead. Thereafter she can be killed. If the player threatens her, the only way to get the locket is to kill her. The player does not need the locket though, as there is another path to take.

This character is removed when the main plot of the quest is done. An info trigger can be left for continuity if desired, explaining that it looks like she left in a hurry, likely under the guard of Vengaul.
